And the problems in the municipality are also concrete and urban.
Earlier in the year, the military was called to the rescue to fight drug gangs in the neighborhoods, and violence against women is particularly serious.
In a disaster area, the bodies of dozens of women murdered in the past two years have been found on the edge of the landfill.
